<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Poser une question</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --ink: #1a1a2e;
      --ink-light: #4a4a6a;
      --ink-muted: #9090aa;
      --cream: #faf9f6;
      --gold: #c9a96e;
      --gold-light: #e8d5b0;
      --border: #e0ddd6;
      --white: #ffffff;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    /* Subtle background texture */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(201,169,110,0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(26,26,46,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 48px 44px 44px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 560px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(26,26,46,0.05), 0 20px 60px rgba(26,26,46,0.08);
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Gold accent top bar */
    .card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold-light), var(--gold), var(--gold-light));
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .icon-wrap {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-light), var(--gold));
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(201,169,110,0.3);
    }

    .icon-wrap svg {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.85rem;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .subtitle {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .field {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both;
    }
    .field:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .field:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.18s; }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink-light);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .input-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }

    textarea, input[type="text"] {
      width: 100%;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--cream);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      outline: none;
      resize: none;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    textarea { min-height: 130px; }

    textarea::placeholder, input::placeholder {
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    textarea:focus, input:focus {
      border-color: var(--gold);
      background: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(201,169,110,0.12);
    }

    .char-count {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 10px;
      right: 14px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin: 28px 0;
    }

    .actions {
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.26s both;
    }

    button[type="submit"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 15px 24px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--white);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a96e, #b8924f);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, filter 0.15s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(201,169,110,0.4);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    button[type="submit"]::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    button[type="submit"]:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(201,169,110,0.5);
      filter: brightness(1.05);
    }

    button[type="submit"]:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(201,169,110,0.35);
    }

    .footer-note {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.32s both;
    }

    .footer-note a {
      color: var(--gold);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .footer-note a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="icon-wrap">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Proposez une question</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Faites entendre votre voix : votre question pourrait être mise à l’honneur dans l’émission sarki Excellence.</p>
  </div>

  <form action="<%= questions_path %>" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token" value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>" />
    <div class="field">
      <label for="content">Votre question</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <textarea
          id="content"
          name="question[content]"
          rows="5"
          placeholder="Décrivez votre question en détail…"
          maxlength="1000"
          oninput="updateCount(this, 'count-content', 1000)"
        ></textarea>
        <span class="char-count" id="count-content">0 / 1000</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <label for="reponse">La réponse</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <textarea
          id="reponse"
          name="question[reponse]"
          rows="5"
          placeholder="Donnez la réponse en détail…"
          maxlength="1000"
          oninput="updateCount(this, 'count-reponse', 1000)"
        ></textarea>
        <span class="char-count" id="count-reponse">0 / 1000</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    
    <div class="field">
      <label for="source">Source de la question</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <input
          type="text"
          id="source"
          name="question[source]"
          placeholder="Ex : documentation, collègue, site web…"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider"/>

    <div class="actions">
      <button type="submit">Envoyer la question →</button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <p class="footer-note">Besoin d'aide ? <a href="#">Consultez la FAQ</a></p>
</div>

<script>
  function updateCount(el, countId, max) {
    document.getElementById(countId).textContent = el.value.length + ' / ' + max;
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>